2016年6月28日土耳其[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]][[阿塔蒂尔克国际机场|阿塔图尔克国际机场]]2号航站楼发生爆炸和枪击袭击。<ref name="bbc">{{cite web|title=Blast and gunfire 'at Istanbul airport'|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36658187|website=bbc.com|publisher=英国广播公司|accessdate=2016年6月28日}}</ref>袭击至少造成除袭击者外的42人死亡、239人受伤。<ref name="rt" /><ref name="NYTImes">{{cite news|last1=Tavernise|first1=Sabrina|last2=Yeginsu|first2=Ceylan|title=Attack at Istanbul Airport Leaves at Least 31 Dead|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/29/world/europe/turkey-istanbul-airport-explosions.html|accessdate=2016年6月29日|work=纽约时报|date=2016年6月28日|archive-date=2018年12月24日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224205151/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/29/world/europe/turkey-istanbul-airport-explosions.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="dailymail">{{cite web|last1=Calderwood|first1=Imogen|title=BREAKING NEWS: Two explosions and gunfire at Istanbul's Ataturk airport cause multiple injuries|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3664710/Two-explosions-gunfire-Istanbul-s-Ataturk-airport-cause-multiple-injuries.html|website=dailymail.co.uk|publisher=每日邮报|accessdate=2016年6月28日|archive-date=2016年6月28日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628202009/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3664710/Two-explosions-gunfire-Istanbul-s-Ataturk-airport-cause-multiple-injuries.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>土耳其总理[[比纳利·耶伊尔德勒姆|比纳利·耶伊尔德勒姆]]表示有迹象显示此次袭击疑似为极端组织[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]所为。<ref name="is">{{cite news|title=土机场遭袭：总理称初步证据指向IS 有外国人遇难|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/06-29/7920984.shtml|accessdate=2016年6月29日|agency=中新社|publisher=中新网|date=2016年6月29日|archive-date=2016年8月16日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816053009/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/06-29/7920984.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>而据[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]6月30日报道，袭击者来自[[后苏联国家|后苏联国家]]，一名俄罗斯人来自[[北高加索|北高加索]]地区，其他人则来自[[乌兹别克斯坦|乌兹别克斯坦]]和[[吉尔吉斯斯坦|吉尔吉斯斯坦]]<ref name="BBC -attackers ID - 30 June">{{cite news|title=Istanbul airport attackers 'Russian, Uzbek and Kyrgyz' - BBC News|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36670576|accessdate=2016-06-30|work=BBC News|date=2016-06-30|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630115125/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36670576|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前据报道袭击者向出租车司机说的一种他不熟悉的语言可能是[[车臣语|车臣语]]<ref>CBS Evening News, 2016-06-29</ref>。

枪击发生在机场的停车场<ref name="bbc" />，而爆炸则出现在国际出发大厅<ref>{{cite web|title=中国驻土耳其使领馆积极协助在土中国公民及华人华侨等应对恐怖袭击|url=http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/ce/cetur/chn/xwdt/t1376190.htm|website=fmprc.gov.cn|accessdate=2016-07-01|date=2016年6月29日|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817040511/http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/ce/cetur/chn/xwdt/t1376190.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-36658187|title=Istanbul Ataturk airport attack: At least 10 reported dead|work=BBC News|access-date=2016-06-28|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628202431/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-36658187|dead-url=no}}</ref>，疑似由[[自杀攻击|自杀式炸弹袭击者]]引爆<ref name="rt" />。有报道称机场不同地点都发生爆炸<ref name="dailymail" />。三名嫌犯在航站楼内或附近引爆他们的炸药。然而，另有报道和目击者指出有四名武装分子逃避爆炸，但未得到警方人员的证实。一名美国情报消息人士向[[CBS_News|CBS News]]透露，这次联合袭击只用了约90秒<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/turkey-istanbul-airport-attack-video-shows-security-take-down-gunman-isis-signs/|title=Istanbul airport attack: Video shows security officers take down gunman before explosion|access-date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702022254/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/turkey-istanbul-airport-attack-video-shows-security-take-down-gunman-isis-signs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
伊斯坦堡於2016年上半年經歷了3次[[恐怖主义|恐怖攻擊]]，包括[[2016年1月伊斯坦布尔爆炸事件|1月]]及[[2016年3月伊斯坦布尔爆炸案|3月]]的自殺攻擊，兩者皆與[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]（ISIS）有關；而6月初的[[2016年6月伊斯坦堡爆炸案|爆炸案]]則係{{link-en|庫爾德自由之鷹|Kurdistan Freedom Falcons}}聲稱其所為，該組織與[[库尔德斯坦工人党|库尔德斯坦工人党]]有所關連<ref name=20160229al-monitor>{{cite news|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2016/02/turkey-outlawed-tak-will-not-deviate-line-of-ocalan.html|title=Outlawed TAK Will Not Deviate Line of Öcalan(PKK)|date=2016-02-29|work=Al-Monitor|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701045608/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2016/02/turkey-outlawed-tak-will-not-deviate-line-of-ocalan.html|archivedate=2016-07-01|df=|accessdate=2016-06-30}}</ref><ref name="guardian">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/07/istanbul-explosion-injuries-after-bus-stop-blast|title=Istanbul blast: 11 dead in bomb attack on police vehicle|date=2016-06-07|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224205051/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/07/istanbul-explosion-injuries-after-bus-stop-blast|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

事发后国际领先媒体普遍注意到事件拥有伊斯兰国恐怖袭击的所有特征，猜测土耳其此番为前总理和现任总统[[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安]]故意对伊斯兰国威胁视而不见付出代价<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/29/turkey-pays-price-erdogan-blindness-to-isis-threat|title=Turkey paying a price for Erdoğan's wilful blindness to Isis threat|date=2016-06-30|accessdate=2016-06-30|publisher=The Guardian|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629150716/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/29/turkey-pays-price-erdogan-blindness-to-isis-threat|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前成为武装分子加入伊斯兰国中转国的土耳其开始觉得对组织采取更强硬路线感到愤怒<ref name='Times oped 6-30'>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/30/world/middleeast/turkey-a-conduit-for-fighters-joining-isis-begins-to-feel-its-wrath.html|title=Turkey, a Conduit for Fighters Joining ISIS, Begins to Feel Its Wrath|date=2016-06-29|accessdate=2016-06-30|publisher=New York Times|archive-date=2016-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160703021300/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/30/world/middleeast/turkey-a-conduit-for-fighters-joining-isis-begins-to-feel-its-wrath.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。也有人指出事件“也许并非偶然，仅仅是最近伊斯兰国在土耳其国内发动的一系列袭击的其中一起，它的出现刚好碰上该国冲动和日益独裁的总统修补他的政权破旧外交关系的时机<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/the-horror-in-istanbul/2016/06/29/56695248-3e0c-11e6-80bc-d06711fd2125_story.html|title=What the horror in Istanbul reveals about the fight against the Islamic State|date=2016-06-29|accessdate=2016-06-30|publisher=Washington Post|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630013558/https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/the-horror-in-istanbul/2016/06/29/56695248-3e0c-11e6-80bc-d06711fd2125_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

7月1日，有报道引述一名身居高位的美国国会议员的话，表示袭击是由一为车臣极端分子艾哈迈德·查塔耶夫（{{lang|en|Akhmed Chatayev}}）策划的。美国德克萨斯州众议院议员、国土安全委员会（{{lang|en|House Committee on Homeland Security}}）主席[[麦克·麦克考|麦克·麦克考]]表示查塔耶夫主导了此次袭击。土耳其和瑞典媒体也认定主脑为查塔耶夫。2008年，查塔耶夫被裁定犯有将武器走私到瑞典的罪，在瑞典监狱服刑9个月<ref>{{cite news|title=US congressman: Chechen extremist behind Istanbul attack|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/fad6ca6eda9142bead29b11b7b259981/turkish-official-mastermind-feb-terror-attack-killed|accessdate=2016-07-01|agency=Associated Press|date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701080109/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/fad6ca6eda9142bead29b11b7b259981/turkish-official-mastermind-feb-terror-attack-killed|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据{{le|阿纳多卢新闻社|Anadolu Agency}}消息，三名袭击者中的两名被认定为拉奇姆·布加诺夫（{{lang|en|Rakim Bulgarov}}）和瓦季姆·奥斯曼诺夫（{{lang|en|Vadim Osmanov}}）<ref name="2 attackers identified - CNN">{{cite news|last1=Faith|first1=Karimi|last2=Steve|first2=Almasy|title=2 Istanbul airport bombers identified, state media says|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/01/europe/turkey-istanbul-ataturk-airport-attack/|accessdate=2016-07-01|work=CNN|date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701084957/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/01/europe/turkey-istanbul-ataturk-airport-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 过程 ==
[[File:Atatürk_international_airport_borak.jpg|thumb]]

当地时间晚上10点左右，两名袭击者接近一个安检点的X射线扫描仪，开枪射击<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/explosions-rock-istanbul-airport-multiple-injuries-reported-n600561|date=28 June 2016|title=Explosions Rock Istanbul Airport, Multiple Deaths Reported|first1=Aziz|last1=Akyavas|first2=Richard|last2=Engel|first3=Robert|last3=Windrem|first4=Alex|last4=Johnson|first5=Erik|last5=Ortiz|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=2016-06-28|archive-date=2019-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829233412/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/explosions-rock-istanbul-airport-multiple-injuries-reported-n600561|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方人员随后还击，袭击者遂引爆自己身上的炸弹<ref name="bbc" /><ref>{{cite news|title=Turkey airport attack: Ten dead after explosions and gunfire reported at Ataturk International airport in Istanbul|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/turkey-ataturk-airport-attack-explosions-gunfire-latest-a7108241.html|website=independent.co.uk|publisher=The Independent|accessdate=2016-06-28|author=Matt Payton|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628202107/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/turkey-ataturk-airport-attack-explosions-gunfire-latest-a7108241.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

根据[[闭路电视|监控录像]]，距离位于2号航站楼（国际候机楼）约24米处的炸弹袭击者引爆了身上的自杀式炸弹<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snappytv.com/tc/2260357|title=Istanbul Airport Attack|website=www.snappytv.com|access-date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2019-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190310032313/http://www.snappytv.com/tc/2260357|dead-url=no}}</ref>。从监控录像可以看到有一群人靠近或卷入爆炸<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snappytv.com/tc/2260357|title=CNN Video CCTV of Istanbul Airport attacks|work=Snappy TV|access-date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2019-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190310032313/http://www.snappytv.com/tc/2260357|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据认为航站楼街对面的停车场也发生一起爆炸<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/29/world/europe/turkey-istanbul-airport-explosions.html|title=Attack at Istanbul Airport Leaves at Least 36 Dead|last=Tavernise|first=Tim Arango, Sabrina|date=28 June 2016|last2=Yeginsu|first2=Ceylan|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224205151/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/29/world/europe/turkey-istanbul-airport-explosions.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。录像显示，一位武装袭击者步行枪击航站楼内的人群。枪手随后被安保人员开枪击中并倒在地上，安保人员上前调查。安保人员估计注意到了枪手的炸药腰带，于是跑开。自杀腰带随后引爆<ref name="CCTV - independent">{{cite news|title=CCTV footage shows moment police officer tackles Istanbul suicide bomber|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/istanbul-airport-attack-video-cctv-footage-shows-moment-police-officer-tackles-suicide-bomber-a7108636.html|accessdate=2016-06-29|work=The Independent|date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629083217/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/istanbul-airport-attack-video-cctv-footage-shows-moment-police-officer-tackles-suicide-bomber-a7108636.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两名袭击者引爆爆炸装备自杀，其中预计一人被安全部队击毙<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/06/28/europe/turkey-istanbul-airport-attacks/index.html|title=Istanbul airport explosions: 28 dead, 60 injured, Turkish official says|author=Gul Tuysuz, Mohammed Tawfeeq and Steve Almasy|work=CNN|access-date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629040546/http://www.cnn.com/2016/06/28/europe/turkey-istanbul-airport-attacks/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另据报道，四名武装分子被看到在爆炸后逃离现场<ref name="rt"/>。

袭击前后，机场内有数百名乘客和群众在商店、厕所或长凳下就地躲藏<ref>{{cite news|title=Passengers flee, hide at Istanbul airport - CNN Video|url=http://www.cnn.com/videos/world/2016/06/28/turkey-airport-istanbul-passengers-flee-orig-mg.cnn|accessdate=2016-06-29|work=CNN|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701091557/http://www.cnn.com/videos/world/2016/06/28/turkey-airport-istanbul-passengers-flee-orig-mg.cnn|dead-url=no}}</ref>。许多旅客向记者讲述了他们在袭击期间目击到的情景。一人表示：“我们正来到国际候机楼，便看到一名男子肆意开枪。他就这样向他面前的人开枪。他穿着一身的黑衣服，没有遮面。我离他50米远。”他继续说道，“我们躲在售票柜台后，但我站起来看到他。两次爆炸过后没多久又发生爆炸。那时时候他已经停止开枪。”最后，他表示：“他转过身向我们走来。他把枪藏在他的夹克里，焦急地环顾四周，留意是否有人打算阻止他，然后走下扶梯......我们又听到了几声枪响，之后又发生爆炸，之后就结束了<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/news/world/2016/06/29/attacker-randomly-opened-fire-before-istanbul-airport-blasts--witness/|title=Attacker 'randomly opened fire' before Istanbul airport blasts - witness - World {{!}} The Star Online|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-date=2017-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170920044346/http://www.thestar.com.my/news/world/2016/06/29/attacker-randomly-opened-fire-before-istanbul-airport-blasts--witness/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”而航站楼外另有人表示[[出租车|出租车]]司机曾从车窗对进入大楼的车龙大喊：“别进去，有炸弹爆炸了！”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/istanbul-ataturk-airport-attack/witness-accounts-deadly-explosions-spread-panic-through-istanbul-airport-n600726|title=Deadly Explosions Spread Panic Through Istanbul Airport|accessdate=2016-06-28|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628232212/http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/istanbul-ataturk-airport-attack/witness-accounts-deadly-explosions-spread-panic-through-istanbul-airport-n600726|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

