==影响==
[[File:Ataturk_airport_Istanbul_01589.jpg|thumb]]

爆炸发生后，所有出港航班取消，但抵港航班继续运行一段时间，直至转机。据[[Flightradar24|Flightradar24]]显示，大多数去往伊斯坦布尔的航班须转往[[伊兹密尔|伊兹密尔]]和[[安卡拉|安卡拉]]。案发后，[[美国联邦航空管理局|美国联邦航空管理局]]取消了所有进出美国的土耳其航班达五个小时<ref name=upi8491467142>{{cite web|url=http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2016/06/28/At-least-36-killed-in-Istanbul-terror-attack-FAA-suspends-US-flights-to-from-Atatrk-airport/8491467142543/|title=At least 36 killed in Istanbul terror attack; FAA suspends U.S. flights to, from Atatürk Airport|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629105224/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2016/06/28/At-least-36-killed-in-Istanbul-terror-attack-FAA-suspends-US-flights-to-from-Atatrk-airport/8491467142543/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，只允许10架在袭击期间已经升空的航班登陆美国。所有被取消的航班是[[土耳其航空|土耳其航空]]的航班<ref name=go40200395>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/scheduled-flights-us-istanbul-temporarily-suspended-terrorist-attack/story?id=40200395|title=US-Istanbul Flights Briefly Suspended After Terrorist Attack|last=News|first=A. B. C.|date=29 June 2016|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629173816/http://abcnews.go.com/International/scheduled-flights-us-istanbul-temporarily-suspended-terrorist-attack/story?id=40200395|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据认为，袭击期间各大航空公司有8到14架航班在航站楼，没有航班在袭击中遭遇危险或被破坏。

袭击发生后最初几个小时，其他国际机场都加强安保力度。在美国，各大国际机场都加强安保以应对阿塔图尔克机场袭击，如[[约翰·F·肯尼迪国际机场|约翰·F·肯尼迪国际机场]]、[[拉瓜迪亚机场|拉瓜迪亚机场]]和[[亚特兰大哈兹菲尔德-杰克逊国际机场|亚特兰大哈兹菲尔德-杰克逊国际机场]]等几大世界上最繁忙的机场。警方表示美国主要机场未收到可信的威胁，但有几个人可能产生威胁<ref name=fox10phoenix167566046>{{citeweb|title=US airports step up security following Turkey attack|author=Jones, Marcy|url=http://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/arizona-news/167566046-story|accessdate=2016-06-29|publisher=Fox 10 Phoenix|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701145020/http://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/arizona-news/167566046-story|archive-date=2016-07-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=nbcnews601106>{{cite web|author=Ken Dilanian and Andrew Blankstein|title=After Istanbul Attack, Security Stepped Up at U.S. Airports for Holiday|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/istanbul-ataturk-airport-attack/after-istanbul-attack-security-stepped-u-s-airports-holiday-n601106|accessdate=2016-06-29|publisher=NBC|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629205633/http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/istanbul-ataturk-airport-attack/after-istanbul-attack-security-stepped-u-s-airports-holiday-n601106|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印尼几大国际机场，如[[雅加达|雅加达]][[苏加诺-哈达国际机场|苏加诺-哈达国际机场]]都收紧安保。印尼交通部长伊瓜纳修·佐南（Ignasius Jonan）指出，印尼各大机场的安全警戒级别都达到“黄色”，这意味着机场“有可能”受到袭击。他还补充道，印尼主要港口也提高安保力度<ref name=tempo173784087>{{cite web|title=Efek Bom di Turki, Bandara di Indonesia Berstatus Kuning|url=https://m.tempo.co/read/news/2016/06/29/173784087/efek-bom-di-turki-bandara-di-indonesia-berstatus-kuning|accessdate=2016-06-29|publisher=''TEMP''O|archive-date=2016-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721212444/https://m.tempo.co/read/news/2016/06/29/173784087/efek-bom-di-turki-bandara-di-indonesia-berstatus-kuning|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度苏哈尔[[贾特拉帕蒂·希瓦吉国际机场|贾特拉帕蒂·希瓦吉国际机场]]、[[2008年孟买连环恐怖袭击|2008年孟买连环恐怖袭击]]现场[[泰姬陵酒店|泰姬陵酒店]]、圣克鲁斯的国内机场都加强安保<ref>{{cite web|title=Security stepped up at airports, Taj hotel after call warns of terror attack|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-news-india/mumbai-airport-taj-hotel-on-alert-after-terror-threat/|accessdate=2016-06-29|work=The Indian Express|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708041035/http://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-news-india/mumbai-airport-taj-hotel-on-alert-after-terror-threat/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[加尔各答|加尔各答]]的[[内塔吉·苏巴斯·钱德拉·鲍斯国际机场|内塔吉·苏巴斯·钱德拉·鲍斯国际机场]]也加强安保<ref>{{citeweb|title=Security stepped up at Kolkata airport|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/kolkata-airport-security-tightened-istanbul-terror-attack/1/703366.html|accessdate=2016-06-29|work=India Today|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630165805/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/kolkata-airport-security-tightened-istanbul-terror-attack/1/703366.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在社交媒体上，#PrayForTurkey（为土耳其祈福）成为热门话题。到6月29日，该话题在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上使用超过30万次，人们希望籍此表现对土耳其和受害这的声援。多张回应袭击的照片成为热门，如此前在网络爆红的《[[世界报_(法国)|世界报]]》漫画家Plantu将此前发生过恐袭的比利时和法国联系在一起<ref>{{cite web|title=#PrayForTurkey: Show of solidarity after Istanbul attack|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/blogs-trending-36661096|accessdate=2016-06-29|publisher=BBC|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630223041/http://www.bbc.com/news/blogs-trending-36661096|dead-url=no}}</ref>。出租车将伤者送往最近的医院<ref>{{cite web|title=Istanbul Airport Attack – Wednesday's reactions|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36658187|accessdate=2016-06-30|publisher=BBC|archive-date=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518091409/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36658187|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

爆炸案发生后，世界各地多个建筑都被土耳其国旗颜色照亮，如柏林[[勃兰登堡门|勃兰登堡门]]、巴黎[[埃菲尔铁塔|埃菲尔铁塔]]、[[阿姆斯特丹王宫|阿姆斯特丹王宫]]、伦敦[[温布利球场|温布利球场]]<ref>{{cite tweet |user=wembleystadium |number=748210228785717249 |date=2016-06-29 |title=The #Wembley arch will tonight be lit red in support of all those affected by last night's attack in Istanbul }}</ref>、科威特[[科威特塔|科威特塔]]、[[莫斯塔尔古桥|莫斯塔尔古桥]]、堪培拉[[澳洲国会大厦|澳洲国会大厦]]和[[墨尔本市政厅|墨尔本市政厅]]<ref name=rt348945>{{cite news|title=From Australia to US, cities light up for Turkey as darkness falls (PHOTOS)|url=https://www.rt.com/viral/348945-cities-turkey-flag-solidarity/|accessdate=2016-06-29|publisher=RT|date=2016-06-28|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630165458/https://www.rt.com/viral/348945-cities-turkey-flag-solidarity/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==各方反應==
=== 国内 ===
[[File:Atatürk_Airport_attack_mourning.jpg|thumb]]
[[土耳其总统|土耳其总统]][[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安]]发表声明，谴责在穆斯林[[斋月|斋月]]发动袭击。他表示本次袭击“表明恐怖主义袭击从不考虑信仰和价值观”，呼吁国际社会采取坚定立场打击恐怖主义，并誓言将加紧土耳其反恐斗争的步伐。埃尔多安还表示：“土耳其有力量、决心和能力将反恐斗争进行到底<ref name=20160628ap>{{cite news|title=The Latest: PM: 36 people, 3 bombers dead in Istanbul attack|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/f25aef07f2a54ed4b7848d9a11f9048c/latest-report-blasts-istanbul-airport-kill-10|accessdate=2016-06-29|agency=Associated Press|date=2016-06-28|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630095009/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/f25aef07f2a54ed4b7848d9a11f9048c/latest-report-blasts-istanbul-airport-kill-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

土耳其宣布6月29日为全国哀悼日。总理部长比纳利·耶尔德勒姆（{{lang|tr|Binali Yıldırım}}）发表声明缅怀袭击遇害者<ref name=hurriyetdailynews101050>{{cite web|title=Turkey declares day of national mourning after Istanbul attack|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/turkey-declares-day-of-national-mourning-after-istanbul-attack.aspx?PageID=238&NID=101050&NewsCatID=341|accessdate=2016-06-29|publisher=''Hurriyet Daily News''|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630172857/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/turkey-declares-day-of-national-mourning-after-istanbul-attack.aspx?pageID=238&nid=101050&NewsCatID=341|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事发期间，原定于对土耳其进行正式访问的[[阿尔巴尼亚总理|阿尔巴尼亚总理]][[埃迪·拉马|埃迪·拉马]]飞机正在降落。他从阿塔图尔克撤回到官邸<ref>{{cite web |title=The Latest: Flights resume from US to Istanbul airport |url=http://www.foxcarolina.com/story/32328403/the-latest-albanian-pm-lands-at-time-of-istanbul-attack |accessdate=2016-06-29 |publisher=Fox Carolina |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630172209/http://www.foxcarolina.com/story/32328403/the-latest-albanian-pm-lands-at-time-of-istanbul-attack |archivedate=2016-06-30 }}</ref>。

6月29日，土耳其当局扣留22名响应袭击的份子，其中13人来自伊斯坦布尔，9人来自沿海城市[[伊兹密尔|伊兹密尔]]。当局证实嫌犯是外国人，具体的讲来自[[乌兹别克斯坦|乌兹别克斯坦]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]的[[車臣共和國|車臣共和國]]和[[吉尔吉斯斯坦|吉尔吉斯斯坦]]<ref>{{citeweb|title=Turkish forces detain 22 in Ataturk Airport terror attack|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/06/30/europe/turkey-istanbul-ataturk-airport-attack/|accessdate=2016-06-29|publisher=''CNN''|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701135013/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/06/30/europe/turkey-istanbul-ataturk-airport-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 国际 ===


